title: Decoding the Jordan Peterson & John Vervaeke conversation, with Paul VanderKlay
description:
Unpacking the Jordan Peterson dialogue with John Vervaeke with Paul VanderKlay.

The dialogue, 'A Conversation so Intense It Might as Well Be Psychedelic' is here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DLg2Q0daphE&t=131s

Films referenced in this conversation include:

John Vervaeke: Flow States and Wisdom: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5jS2AiQEz-E

The Evolving Conversation, John Vervaeke & Peter Limberg: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FQ3c3niLvbI&t=3s

After the Meaning Crisis, John Vervaeke: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yz6qgfjGMAg&t=206s
